name: World's Largest MUSEUM OF PINBALL - Help Us Launch!
blurb: Pinball is experiencing a NATIONAL COMEBACK! Help us take the game (or sport) to an even wider audience thru the Museum of Pinball.

rewards.reward: No Reward

I CAN'T MAKE IT TO THE GRAND OPENING, BUT I WANT TO BE ON THE WALL OF SUPPORTERS. Every $10 counts, and we greatly appreciate it! We'll list your name on the Wall of Supporters and play a game of pinball for you.

ONE DAY GUEST PASS - You will be listed on the Guest List for entry on any day of your choosing AFTER the Grand Opening Weekend of the Museum of Pinball. Plus, your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters to be displayed in the Museum entrance area. NOTE: This Guest Pass can NOT be used on the weekend of the Grand Opening, and it has no expiration date.

10 FOUNDING PARTNER TOKENS \u2013 10 Limited Edition Museum of Pinball tokens (\u201cFounding Partner\u201d tokens only available to Kickstarter supporters and destined to be the most collectible we\u2019ll ever produce), and your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

SUNDAY GRAND OPENING ONLY (3rd Day Early Entry) \u2013 Be part of pinball history! You will be listed on the Guest List for the 2nd day of the Grand Opening Weekend (January/February 2014 - exact date TBA) of the Museum of Pinball. Plus, your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters to be displayed in the Museum entrance area.

\u201cPINBALL TIL I DIE\u201d T-SHIRT \u2013 T-shirt with \u201cPinball Til I Die\u201d on the front (premium quality t-shirt in the size of your choice) - see design below to the left, and your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters to be displayed in the Museum entrance area.

SATURDAY GRAND OPENING ONLY (2nd Day Early Entry) \u2013 Be part of pinball history! You will be listed on the Guest List with early entry to the Grand Opening on Saturday (January/February 2014 - exact date TBA) of the Museum of Pinball. Plus, your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters to be displayed in the Museum entrance area.

LIMITED EDITION \u201cMUSEUM OF PINBALL\u201d T-SHIRT \u2013 Limited Edition Museum of Pinball t-shirt (premium quality t-shirt in the size of your choice - only available to Kickstarter supporters) - see design below to the left. Shipping within the US included.

FRIDAY GRAND OPENING GALA ONLY \u2013 Be part of pinball history! You will be listed on the Guest List to the Grand Opening Gala on Friday evening (January/February 2014 - exact date TBA) of the Museum of Pinball. Plus, your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters to be displayed in the Museum entrance area.

3-DAY GRAND OPENING WEEKEND PASS \u2013 Be part of pinball history! You will be listed on the Guest List with full access to the Grand Opening Weekend including Friday night, Saturday, and Sunday (January/February 2014 - exact date TBA) of the Museum of Pinball. Plus, your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters to be displayed in the Museum entrance area.

TNT COMBO = TWO T-SHIRTS + 10 FOUNDING PARTNER TOKENS \u2013 Receive 10 Limited Edition Museum of Pinball tokens, the "Pinball Til I Die" t-shirt, and the Limited Edition Museum of Pinball t-shirt (premium quality t-shirt in the size of your choice), and your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

THE POWER PLAY = TWO T-SHIRTS, 10 FOUNDING PARTNER TOKENS, and 3-DAY GRAND OPENING WEEKEND PASS \u2013 Receive 10 Limited Edition Museum of Pinball tokens, the "Pinball Til I Die" t-shirt, and the Limited Edition Museum of Pinball t-shirt (premium quality t-shirt in the size of your choice). You will be listed on the Guest List with full access to the Grand Opening Weekend including Friday night, Saturday, and Sunday (January/February 2014 - exact date TBA) of the Museum of Pinball. Plus, your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

PINBALL COVER + THE POWER PLAY \u2013 High-quality black canvas pinball cover (your choice of Standard or Widebody), and you will receive everything listed in THE POWER PLAY (two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass). Plus, your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

DOUBLE POWER PLAY = TWO PEOPLE GET TWO T-SHIRTS, 10 FOUNDING PARTNER TOKENS, and 3-DAY GRAND OPENING WEEKEND PASS \u2013 Both people (2 friends or a couple) each receive 10 Limited Edition Museum of Pinball tokens, the "Pinball Til I Die" t-shirt, and the Limited Edition Museum of Pinball t-shirt (premium quality t-shirt in the size of your choice). Both people will be listed on the Guest List with full access to the Grand Opening Weekend including Friday night, Saturday, and Sunday (January/February 2014 - exact date TBA) of the Museum of Pinball. Plus, both names will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

PINBALL SKATES / DOLLY + THE POWER PLAY \u2013 A pair of high-quality pinball skates / dolly to move most pinball machines, and , and you will receive everything listed in THE POWER PLAY (two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass). Plus, your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

ADOPT a PINBALL MACHINE + THE POWER PLAY \u2013 We will place a custom plaque above the pinball machine of your choice with your name, company name, the name of a loved one, or a phrase of your choice (family friendly only) to remain in place for two years, and we\u2019ll do our best to accommodate your first choice of machines. Plus, you will receive everything listed in THE POWER PLAY (two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass), and your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

PINBALL ROTISSERIE STAND + THE POWER PLAY \u2013 High-quality pinball rotisserie stand to work on playfields. Plus, you will receive everything listed in THE POWER PLAY (two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass), and your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

"FRIEND" SPONSOR + THE POWER PLAY \u2013 One full-color 2 feet x 4 feet sponsorship sign to advertise your company will be strategically placed in the Museum for one year, and a small logo will be placed on website and inserted in our monthly e-newsletter two times. Plus, you will receive everything listed in THE POWER PLAY (two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass), and you will be recognized as a \u201cFriend\u201d on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping worldwide included.

"ASSOCIATE" SPONSOR + THE POWER PLAY \u2013  Two full-color 2 feet x 4 feet sponsorship signs to advertise your company will be strategically placed in the Museum for one year, and a medium logo will be placed on website and inserted in our monthly e-newsletter two times. Plus, you will receive everything listed in THE POWER PLAY (two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass), and you will be recognized as a \u201cAssociate\u201d on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping worldwide included.

ULTIMATE PINBALLER LOUNGE + 6 POWER PLAYS \u2013 Bring 5 of your friends (plus you) and hang out in your own exclusive "Pinballer" lounge (approx. 12 feet x 12 feet room), and we'll provide up to two games of your choice from a list of 100 to be enjoyed the entire Grand Opening Weekend (Friday night, Saturday, or Sunday). We'll do our best to accommodate your first choice of games, and we'll provide an assortment of snacks and sodas each day. The 6 POWER PLAYS (each includes two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass) will be shipped to one address for you to distribute as you like. In addition, your name will be listed as a VIP on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within US included.

"PARTNER" SPONSOR + 2 POWER PLAYS - Five full-color 2 feet x 4 feet sponsorship signs to advertise your company will be strategically placed in the Museum for one year, and a medium logo will be placed on website and inserted in our monthly e-newsletter four times. The 2 POWER PLAYS (each includes two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass) will be shipped to one address for you to distribute as you like. In addition, your name will be listed as a "Partner" on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping worldwide included.

PRIVATE PINBALL PARTY \u2013 We\u2019ll host a private pinball party for your group (up to 1,000 people for up to 8 hours) which includes unlimited play on all machines (excludes Friday-Sunday). We\u2019ll schedule the event on a date of your choice after the Grand Opening in January 2014.

GOLDEN TICKET + PARKING SPACE + POWER PLAY - For 5 years, you will NEVER HAVE TO PAY admission or for premium game play.This prestigious reward will gain you admission into the Museum of Pinball during regular business hours and any special events that we host such as the Grand Opening Weekend and tournaments. (Of course, this wouldn't include private parties hosted by outside organizations such as parties or corporate events.) You will also have your own Reserved Parking Space (with your name on it) and access to the Executive Lavatory. Plus, you will receive everything listed in THE POWER PLAY (two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass), and your name will be listed on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

"EXHIBIT" SPONSOR + 10 POWER PLAYS - Two full-color 2 feet x 4 feet sponsorship signs (one at the entrance and one at the exit of one historical exhibit) for one year. For one year, a medium-sized logo will be placed on our website and inserted in monthly e-newsletter four times. When referring to the particular exhibit, it will be advertised as \u201csponsored by ______________\u201d for one year. The 10 POWER PLAYS (each including two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass) will be shipped to one address for you to distribute as you like. In addition, your name will be listed as an "Exhibit" Sponsor on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping worldwide included.

GRAND OPENING VIP (VERY IMPORTANT PINBALLER) \u2013 We\u2019ll fly you from anywhere in the Continental US to be our guest at the Grand Opening Weekend (January 2014) \u2013 including two nights hotel accommodations, personal driver, and pick-up via limo to the Friday Grand Opening Gala. (During your stay, food will be on your own.) You will receive everything listed in THE POWER PLAY (two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass), and you\u2019ll have your choice of a pinball machine to \u201cadopt\u201d (full info above). In addition, your name will be listed as a VIP on the Wall of Supporters. Shipping within the US included.

"SILVER" SPONSOR + 10 POWER PLAYS \u2013 Two 4 feet x 8 feet full-color mini-billboards will be placed prominently within the Museum for two years. For two years, a medium-sized logo will be placed on our website and inserted in monthly e-newsletter six times. You will also receive 10 Season Passes (free access for one year), and 100 Guest Passes (single use on any day AFTER the Grand Opening). Choose one person to be in the ribbon cutting group photo at the Grand Opening Weekend. The 10 POWER PLAYS (each includes two T-shirts, 10 Founding Partner Tokens, and a 3-Day Grand Opening Weekend Pass) will be shipped to one address for you to distribute as you like. In addition, you will receive a Private Pinball Party, the opportunity to adopt a pinball machine, your name will be listed as a "Silver" Sponsor on the Wall of Supporters, and we'll kiss you on the lips (if you wish). Shipping worldwide included.
